api_list.name: Wrestling News
api_list.description: This will give you the most up to date results for wrestling matches.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://wrestling-api.p.rapidapi.com/{wrestling}"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "wrestling-api.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
